  "title": "HR & ADMIN EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Jobscope for HR</strong></em></p>\n<p>· Update and maintain staff personal records in hard copies and digital files;</p>\n<p>· Prepare and keep record employment agreement;</p>\n<p>· Recruitment, orientation of new staffs,</p>\n<p>· Arrange training courses for workers</p>\n<p>· Conduct probationary and annual performance evaluation exercises;</p>\n<p>· Responsible for payroll;</p>\n<p>· Coordination with company employees with their personal welfare and payroll issues;</p>\n<p>· Apply, renewal and cancel WP/SP;</p>\n<p>· Handling of work injury matters</p>\n<p>· Issue of uniform and PPE to staffs and workers</p>\n<p>· Issue of Festival gifts and allowance to staffs and workers</p>\n<p>· Travel arrangements of staffs</p>\n<p>· Dormitory arrangement and upkeep of proper records</p>\n<p>· Preparation of petty cash claims.</p>",
